    <entry>
      <title>MarkDown语法及Typroa快捷键</title>
      <link href="/2023/06/19/MarkDown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%8ATyproa%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE/"/>
      <url>/2023/06/19/MarkDown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%8ATyproa%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 一级标题        ctrl+1</span><br><span class="line">## 二级标题       ctrl+2</span><br><span class="line">### 三级标题      ctrl+3</span><br><span class="line">#### 四级标题     ctrl+4</span><br><span class="line">##### 五级标题    ctrl+5</span><br><span class="line">###### 六级标题   ctrl+6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>注意： #后+空格</strong></p><h1 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">```</span><br><span class="line">int main()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">```</span><br><span class="line">Ctrl+Shift+K</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; “一支穿云箭，千军万马来相见；两副忠义胆，刀山火海提命现。”  —— 星仔   ctrl+Shift+Q</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>“一支穿云箭，千军万马来相见；两副忠义胆，刀山火海提命现。”  —— 星仔</p></blockquote><h1 id="有序列表"><a href="#有序列表" class="headerlink" title="有序列表"></a>有序列表</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">把大象放进冰箱：</span><br><span class="line">1. 打开冰箱</span><br><span class="line">2. 把大象塞进去</span><br><span class="line">3. 关上冰箱</span><br><span class="line">Ctrl+Shift+[</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>把大象放进冰箱：</p><ol><li>打开冰箱</li><li>把大象塞进去</li><li>关上冰箱</li></ol><h1 id="无序列表"><a href="#无序列表" class="headerlink" title="无序列表"></a>无序列表</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PLC的语言：</span><br><span class="line">- 梯形图</span><br><span class="line">- ST</span><br><span class="line">Ctrl+Shift+]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>PLC的语言：</p><ul><li>梯形图</li><li>ST</li></ul><h1 id="任务列表"><a href="#任务列表" class="headerlink" title="任务列表"></a>任务列表</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">明天要做的事：</span><br><span class="line">-[x] 吃饭</span><br><span class="line">-[ ] 睡觉</span><br><span class="line">-[ ] 打游戏</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>明天要做的事：</p><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 吃饭</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 睡觉</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 打游戏</li></ul><h1 id="数学公式"><a href="#数学公式" class="headerlink" title="数学公式"></a>数学公式</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\frac&#123;\partial f&#125;&#123;\partial x&#125; = 2\sqrt&#123;a&#125;x</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">Ctrl+Shift+M</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$$<br>\frac{\partial f}{\partial x} &#x3D; 2\sqrt{a}x<br>$$</p><h1 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">|姓名|年龄|成绩|</span><br><span class="line">|:---|:---:|---:|</span><br><span class="line">|李亚星|26|80|</span><br><span class="line">Ctrl+T</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="left">姓名</th><th align="center">年龄</th><th align="right">成绩</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">李亚星</td><td align="center">26</td><td align="right">80</td></tr></tbody></table><h1 id="脚注"><a href="#脚注" class="headerlink" title="脚注"></a>脚注</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">英韦尔[^1]</span><br><span class="line">[^1]:英韦尔(天津)工业控制技术有限公司于2010年06月02日成立。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>英韦尔[^1]<br>[^1]:英韦尔(天津)工业控制技术有限公司于2010年06月02日成立。</p><h1 id="分割线"><a href="#分割线" class="headerlink" title="分割线"></a>分割线</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="行内元素"><a href="#行内元素" class="headerlink" title="行内元素"></a>行内元素</h1><h2 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[百度](https://www.baidu.com/) Ctrl+K</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com/">百度</a></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[百度](https://www.baidu.com/ &quot;一个搜索引擎&quot;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com/" title="一个搜索引擎">百度</a></p><h2 id="引用链接"><a href="#引用链接" class="headerlink" title="引用链接"></a>引用链接</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[百度][id]</span><br><span class="line">[id]:https://www.baidu.com/ &quot;一个搜索引擎&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com/" title="一个搜索引擎">百度</a></p><h2 id="链接到标题"><a href="#链接到标题" class="headerlink" title="链接到标题"></a>链接到标题</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">请参考[标题1](1.标题)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>请参考<a href="1.%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98">标题1</a></p><h2 id="URL"><a href="#URL" class="headerlink" title="URL"></a>URL</h2><p><a href="http://www.baidu.com/">http://www.baidu.com</a></p><h2 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![](C:\Users\liyaxing\Desktop\PCtm_d9c8750bed0b3c7d089fa7d55720d6cf.png &quot;百度搜索&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">Ctrl+Shift+I</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="C:\Users\liyaxing\Desktop\PCtm_d9c8750bed0b3c7d089fa7d55720d6cf.png" title="百度搜索"></p><h2 id="字体"><a href="#字体" class="headerlink" title="字体"></a>字体</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*斜体*       ctrl+I</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>斜体</em></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">**粗体**     ctrl+B</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>粗体</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">***斜体粗体***</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>斜体粗体</strong></em></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`printf()` </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>printf()</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;u&gt;下划线&lt;/u&gt;  ctrl+U</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><u>下划线</u></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~删除线~~     Alt+Shift+5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><del>删除线</del></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$\thea=x^2$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$\thea&#x3D;x^2$</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">H~2O</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>H~2O</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">X^2^</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>X^2^</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">==高亮文字==</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;高亮文字&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><h1 id="遇到的问题"><a href="#遇到的问题" class="headerlink" title="遇到的问题"></a>遇到的问题</h1><ul><li><p><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>数学公式不能正确显示</strong></p></li><li><p><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>脚注不能正确显示</strong></p></li><li><p><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>任务列表不能正确显示</strong></p></li><li><p><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>链接跳转报错</strong></p><p>链接前加http:&#x2F;&#x2F;</p></li><li><p><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>图片上传问题（相对地址和绝对地址）</strong></p></li><li><p><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>行内数学公式</strong></p></li><li><p><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>下标和上标</strong></p></li><li><p><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>高亮文字不能正常显示</strong></p></li><li><p><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>连接到标题不能正常打开</strong></p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
